{"tid":2193781,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"花木蘭在台灣拿到好成績，一點也不覺驚奇。","createTime":"2020-09-08T05:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T06:04:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07ca17778b1ad9b1afb3ca6ceedaca0caa06853c","tid":2193781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"花木蘭在台灣拿到好成績，一點也不覺驚奇。首先就是台灣是一個非常中國化的地方，花木蘭那種鬼五馬六的美術可能正合不少人口味，就像台北城市景觀的那種後期民國美學，以及很多人投了票支持的韓國瑜美學，第二是其實二戰前也不是很多人在乎集中營，只是軸心國打輸了才一起加入聲討。<br />\n<br />\n香港和台灣的心理距離，其實比一般人想像的更遠，沒有接近到他們會因為劉亦菲支持港警就能夠有效抵制。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\npatreon <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/lewisdada\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Flewisdada&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=f74a45cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/lewisdada</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/204247792994307/posts/3235428773209512/?extid=oL8K7jQcKktc3QVZ&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F204247792994307%2Fposts%2F3235428773209512%2F%3Fextid%3DoL8K7jQcKktc3QVZ%26d%3Dn&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=f32dbba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/204247792994307/posts/3235428773209512/?extid=oL8K7jQcKktc3QVZ&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"43ae3e5e55a3b64bcb451893647b782eb8609db8","tid":2193781,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"在大陸是劣評如潮，其中有些還真的講到一些道理出來，例如，木蘭辭的中心是孝道，不是忠君，廸士尼為了奉迎中國市場，把原本率性自然拍成裝腔作勢，損壞了史詩的美感。。。"}]}